Program: The History Hour
Title: Autism and the MMR vaccine
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswqn0
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 26 Mar 2019
How a British doctor misled the world by linking the MMR vaccine to autism; the early rise of Hungary’s Viktor Orban also what it was like to contest the Soviet Union’s first multi-party elections plus the exposure in the 1970s of a Nazi criminal in Holland and uncovering Mexico’s Aztec past. Photo: Dr Andrew Wakefield arrives at the General Medical Council in London to face a disciplinary panel, July 16th 2007 (Daniel Berehulak/Getty Images) Show less